code: export default function CreateSearchResults(symbolsArray,content,setResults){var tempResults=[];if(content.length===0){setResults([]);return;}var contentToSearch=content.toUpperCase();var leng=symbolsArray.length;for(var i=0;i<leng;i++){var symbolElement=symbolsArray[i];if(symbolElement.symbol[0]===contentToSearch[0]||symbolElement.description[0]===contentToSearch[0]){if(symbolElement.symbol.includes(contentToSearch)||symbolElement.description.includes(contentToSearch)){tempResults.push(symbolElement);}}}setResults(tempResults);}
